docs {
  Creates a new CRM support ticket.
  
  **Body Parameters:**
  * `bookingId` (string): Reference to associated booking (optional).
  * `ticketType` (string): Type of support ticket.
  * `transporterId` (string): Reference to transporter (optional).
  * `priority` (enum): 'low', 'medium', 'high', 'urgent' (default: 'medium').
  * `issueCategory` (string): Category of the issue.
  * `issueSubCategory` (string): Sub-category of the issue (optional).
  * `assignTo` (uuid): User ID of assigned support agent (optional).
  * `subject` (string): Short summary of the issue.
  * `description` (string): Detailed description of the issue.
  * `createdBy` (string): User ID who created the ticket.
  * `status` (enum): 'open', 'in_progress', 'resolved', 'closed', 'cancelled' (default: 'open').
}
